----------------------------------------------

- Handle editable installs (#25)
- Ignore index url parameters in parse_requirements (#25)

0.0.7
----------------------------------------------

- Drop support for Python 3.4
- Add support for pip 19.0, 19.0.1, 19.0.2, 19.0.3

